  4 . Lun7 chhai7 bok8-chu2 , hau3 bok8-chu2 e5 put-thong
  Lun7 put-thong u7 kui2-na7 hang7 e5 ian5- kou3 . Sin5-hun5 boe7 tit-thang lai5 hu7 ti7 sin5- chu2--nih8 . Lang5 tiam3-teh kong2 u7 sin5 tiam3 ti7 sin5-chu2--nih8 , m7-si7 m7-chai-kong2 sin5-hun5 tioh8 khi3 im-kan; i si7 kong2 , lang5 u7 sam-hun5 chhit-phek . Chhit-phek bian2 kong2, kan-ta lun7 sam-hun5 chiu7 ho2 . TaN lang5 kong2 sam-hun5 chiu7-si7 kong2, chit8-tiau5 khi3 im-kan, chit8-tiau5 tiam3 bong7-lai7, chit8-tiau5 hu7 sin5-chu2; taN lang5 thai2- tho2 u7 saN-tiau5 sin5-hun5? Na7 chin-chiaN3 u7 saN-tiau5 sin5-hun5, chiu7 kiam2-chhai2 chit-tiau5 hun5 ai3-beh chiah8 , hit-tiau5 hun5 m7- ai3 chiah8, a2-si7 bo5-beh liam5-piN chiah8 ; a2-si7 chit-tiau5 hun5 ai3 beh khun3 , hit-tiau5 hun5 m7-ai3 khun3 , chiu7 kiam2-m7-tioh8 oan-ke saN-phah mah ? Sou2-i2 se3-siok8 teh kong2 sam-hun5 chiah-e5 tai7-chi3, put-ko3 si7 iN7- toan na7-tiaN7, Ki5-sit8 sin5-hun5 chit8-tiau5 na7-tiaN7, sin5-hun5 ki3-jian5 chit8-tiau5, chiu7 hit-tiau5 khi3 tah-loh8 ? Tiam3 ti7 sin5-chu2 a2 m7-si7 ? M7-si7 ; khi3 im-kan . Lang5 siN- cheng5 kiaN5 ho2 , oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou , sin3 hok-im, tit-tioh8 Kiu3-chu2 e5 siok8-choe7 , ThiN-pe7 e5 sia3-choe7 , Seng3-sin5 e5 teng5-siN , si2-au7 sin- khu kui thou2 , sin5-hun5 chiuN7 thian-tong5 , tit-tioh8 eng2-oan2 e5 hok-khi3 ; siat-su2 choe3 Mou5-kui2 e5 kiaN2, hong3-chhiong3 su-iok8 kiaN5-phaiN2 , chiu7 sin5-hun5 tim5-lun5 te7-gek8 , thai2 oe7 koh siN chit8-tiau5 sin5-hun5 lai5 hu7 ti7 bok8-chu2-ah ? 
  U7 lang5 pok kong2 , Hun5 sui-bong2 chit8- tiau5 na7-tiaN7 , chong2-si7 iu5-goan5 oe7 hu7 ti7 sin5-chu2 ; in-ui7 na7 kiaN5-ho2 , i e5 sin5-hun5 kau3 thian-tong5 iau2-ku2 iah8 oe7 tiam3 ti7 sin5-chu2 ; na7 si7 kiaN5-phaiN2 koaiN ti7 te7-gek8, theng3-hau7 chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 lai5 phah te7-gek8 , phah liau2-au7 i oe7 chhut--lai5 , an2-ni i kiam2-boe7 lai5 hu7 ti7 sin5-chu2 mah ? 
  Goa2 kong2 , M7 si7 an2-ni ; thian-tong5 si7 chiau5-chng5 ho2 , toa7 hok-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7 , se3-kan ong5-kiong a2-si7 te7-it song2 e5 sou2- chai7 kap i iah8 boe7 pi2--tit ; lang5 i2-keng kau3 hit-ui7 , khoaN3 se3-kan te7-it song2 e5 toa7- chhu3 , siong7-chhiaN2 chhin-chhiuN7 pun3-so3 , ho5-hong3 hit-te3 piN2-pang-a2 , i thai2-tho2 beh lai5 tiam3 ? Lun7 kau3 chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 phah te7-gek8 e5 tai7-chi3, si7 koh-khah lam7- sam2 . In-ui7 te7-gek8 si7 bo5 heng5, hit e5 ui7 si7 Siong7-te3 pi7-pan7 teh heng5-hoat8 phaiN2- lang5--e5, ti7-hia thang5 boe7 si2 , he2 boe7 hoa; kiam2-si7 he5-siuN7 sou2 oe7 phoa3--tit mah ? Na7 Siong7-te3 liah8 lang5 koaiN-loh8 te7-gek8 , he5-siuN7 oe7 pang3 i chhut--lai5, an2-ni he5- siuN7 pi2 Siong7-te3 khah-toa7, pai3 he5-siuN7 chiu7 kau3-giah8 . Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 kong2, M7-si7 an2-ni, he5-siuN7 put-ko3 si7 thok put8 ka7 Siong7-te3 kiu5-cheng5 na7-tiaN7 , thai2-tho2 kong2 pi2 Siong7-te3 khah toa7 ? Goa2 kong2 , Iah8 m7-si7 an2-ni ; lang5 hou7 koaN-hu2 liah8- khi3 koaiN-kaN, kiam2-chhai2 khi3 thok ho2 se3- thau5 e5 lang5 khi3 kiu5-cheng5, siong7-chhiaN2 tioh8 khoaN3 i-e5 an3 si7 chaiN2-iuN7, bo5 tek- khak kian3-kiu5 kian3-pang3 ; ho5-hong3 lang5 hou7 Siong7-te3 koaiN, he5-siuN7 thok-put8 , put8 kian3 kiu5 , Siong7-te3 kian3-pang3 . An2-ni lang5 u7 phaiN2, Siong7-te3 bo5 pan7, si7 Siong7- te3 bo5 kong-to7 ; u7 chiN5--e5 chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 phah te7-gek8 , chiu7 oe7 chhut te7-gek8 , bo5 chiN5 thang chhiaN2 he5-siuN7 lai5 phah--e5, chiu7 boe7 chhut te7-gek8 ; an2-ni si7 iu2- chian5-chia2 seng , bu5-chian5-chia2 su2 , khoaN3 Siong7-te3 choe3 tham-koan u-li7, choe7 tang7 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7 ? 
  An2-ni lang5 e5 sin5-hun5 na7 kau3 thian- tong5 iah8 m7-lai5 hu7 ti7 sin5-chu2 , na7 kau3 te7- gek8 chiu7 eng2-eng2 boe7 tit lai5 ; i2-keng boe7 hu7 sin5-chu2, chiah koh lai5 chhong3 sin5-chu2 , che kiam2 m7-si7 put-thong mah ? 
  Koh khah put-thong--e5 , chiu7-si7 u7-e5 si7 chit8-lang5 ia7 u7 kui2-na7 sian sin5-chu2 ; chhin-chhiuN7 Chiang-chiu siok8 u7 chit8 sou2- chai7 siN3 Lim5--e5, kui2-chap8 ni5 cheng5 Tng5- mng5-hoan2 kau3 in chiu7 chhiaN2 sin5-chu2 chau2, u7-e5 chhiaN2 kong e5 sin5-chu2, u7-e5 chhiaN2 ma2 e5 sin5-chu2 ; tui3 si3-soaN3 liau2-au7 bo5 koh choe3 tui , in-ui7 chhiaN2 kong e5 sin5-chu2--e5 kah chhiaN2 ma2 e5 sin5-chu2--e5 tioh8 chhiaN2 ma2 e5 sin5-chu2 lai5 chiu7 in; chhiaN2 ma2--e5 kong2 , Goan2 kah hiah kian3-siau3 cha-bou2 chhe7 lin2 ta-pou ! Tui3 an2-ni , chhiaN2 kong e5 sin5-chu2--e5 tioh8 chhong3 chit8-sin ma2 e5 sin5-chu2, chhiaN2 ma2--e5 , koh chhong3 chit8-sin kong e5 sin5-chu2 . Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, hap8-li2 mah ? Chit8-lang5 kiam2 u7 nng7 e5 sin5 thang hu7 nng7-sin bok8-chu2 ah ? Sit8-chai7 toa7 put- thong . 
  2 . Siat-su2 oe7 lai5 hu7 , i iah8 m7-lai5 . Lang5 sou2 ai3 chhin-kun7--e5 , tek-khak tioh8 i-e5 tang5-lui7 , bo5 tang5-lui7 chiu7 m7 saN-oa2 . Sou2- i2 cha2 eng7 lang5 lai5 choe3 si , tioh8 eng7 ka- ki7 e5 kiaN2-sun chiah oe7 choe3--tit ; si7 in- ui7 kong2 , goa7-siN3 e5 kiaN2-sun m7-si7 ka-ki7 e5 kut-jiok8 hiat-meh8 sou2 chhut--e5, sin5 m7 lai5 oa2 . Chong2-si7 iau2-ku2 si7 lang5, bok8- chu2 si7 chha5 , si2-si2 e5 mih8 , sin5 kam2 beh oa2 ? Siat-su2 beh lai5 oa2 , chhi3-mng7 chit8-te3-a2 e5 pang u7 kau3-giah8 thang hou7 sin5 khia7-khi2 a2-bo5 ? Sou2 kong2 sou2-choe3 long2 si7 bo5 cheng5-li2 bo5 i3-su3 ; lin2 chhai7 bok8-chu2 e5 lang5 , kan2 m7 ka-ki7 seng2-chhat khoaN3 teh ? 
  3 . Lang5 teh chhai7 bok8-chu2 , i3-su3 si7 kong2 na7 bo5 hau3--i , chiu7 oe7 choe3 iau-kui2 . Na7 chin-chiaN3 u7-iaN2, chiu7 tioh8 soa3 choe3 hou7 i chheng7 , in-ui7 bo5 chiah8 oe7 iau , chiu7 bo5 chheng7 oe7 koaN5 . Cheng-siN bo5 chheng7 si7 in-ui7 i u7 mng5, kiam2 lang5 si2-liau2 sin5- hun5 oe7 hoat-mng5 ? Na7 an2-ni si7 khoan2- thai7 chou2-kong choe3 cheng-siN , koh-khah put-hau3 . TaN lin2 chhai7 bok8-chu2--e5 , bat eng7 mih8 hau3 sin5-chu2 , kam2 bat soa3 choe3 saN-a2-khou3 hou7 i chheng7 ; na7-kah boe7 koaN5 chu7-jian5 iah8 boe7 iau , ki3-jian5 boe7 iau chu7- jian5 bian2-che3 , ki3-jian5 bian2-che3 chiu7 soa3 bian2 chhai7 bok8-chu2 si7 beng5 . 
