  1 . Chou2-kong boe7 lai5 chiah8 . 
  Chha5-kho2 cha2 seng3-ong5 seng3-jin5 siat chit-e5 che3 e5 hoat-tou7 , pun2 m7-si7 ui7 chou2- kong , sit8-chai7 si7 ui7-tioh8 kiaN2-sun ; hau3- keng kong2 , ¡§ Khi3 chong-biau7--nih8 ti3- keng3 , si7 beh bo5 boe7-ki3-tit pe7-bu2 ¡¨ . Tan5- kiong kong2, ¡§ Khi2-thau5 si2 , eng7 bah-hu2 sng-chhou3 lai5 koan3-tian7 , tit-beh khi3 tai5 e5 si5 , eng7 ngou2-seng lai5 che3 , tai5-liau2 to3-- lai5 , koh-chai3 hau3 , ( che si7 jit8 tiong-tau3 ti7 i si2 e5 pang5-lai7 hau3, ) be7 bat khoaN3-kiN3 i lai5 chiah8 , tui3 teng2-tai7 i2-lai5 , long2 bo5 pang3-soah , si7 ai3 lang5 bo5 poe7 i e5 chhin . ¡¨ Hong-ki3 kong2, ¡§ Siu-cheng2 chong-biau7 , keng3 che3-su7 , si7 beh ka3 peh-siN3 tui-siuN7 iu2-hau3 . ¡¨ Che beng5-beng5 si7 kong2 , che3 m7-si7 in-ui7 chou2-kong oe7 lai5 chiah8 , put- ko3 si7 hou7 lang5 oe7 siau3-liam7 i e5 chou2-kong na7-tiaN7 . Lun7 si2--e5 boe7 lai5 kam3-lap8 oah8- lang5 e5 che3-su7, beng5-li2--e5, ka-ki7 oe7 chai. Au-iong5 Siu Long5-kong-chhian pian2- ki3--nih8 kong2, ¡§ Che3 chin7-choe7 mih8 , m7- tat8-tioh8 eng7 chio2-chio2 mih8 hou7 pe7-bu2 oah8-oah8 e5 si5 thang chiah8 . ¡¨ Cheng-chu2 kong2 , ¡§ Choe3 kiaN2 e5 lang5 beh hong7-iong7 , pe7-bu2 to boe7 theng3-hau7--tit , ( i3-su3 si7 si2 , ) sou2-i2 thai5-gu5 lai5 che3 , m7 tat8-tioh8 than3 pe7-bu2 te7-teh eng7 koe ti lai5 hou7 i chiah8 khah- ho2 . ¡¨ Chiah-e5 beng5-beng5 si7 kong2, che3- su7 m7-si7 beh-hou7 chou2-kong lai5 chiah8, put- ko3 si7 beh hou7 lang5 bo5 boe7-ki3-tit i e5 pe7-bu2 na7-tiaN7 . Chai7 sian-ong5 lip8-che3 e5 pun2- i3 si7 kong2-kio3 pe7-bu2 si7 pun2-goan5, pe7-bu2 si2 chiu7 pun2-goan5 choat8; pun2-goan5 kah choat8 , chiu7 iu2-hau3 e5 sim iah8 choat8 ; m7- ku2 pe7-bu2 si7 chit8-si3-lang5 sou2 tioh8 siau3- liam7--e5, sou2-i2 choe3 che3 e5 hoat-tou7, hou7 lang5 ti7 choat8-hau3 e5 tiong-kan boe7 liam5-piN choat8, si7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 eng7 chit-e5 che3 choe3 cheng2, chai ti7 lang5 e5 sim, hou7 lang5 oe7 siN-chhut iu2-hau3; lip8-che3 e5 pun2-i3 put-ko3 si7 an2-ni. Kho2-sioh au7-tai7 e5 thak8-chheh lang5 , bo5 beng5-pek8 sian-ong5 lip8-che3 e5 i3-su3, lam7-sam2 kong2 kau3 hiah- e5 im-iong5, li2-khi3 , chou2-kong lai5 kam3-lap8 e5 tai7-chi3 , soa3 siat peh-siN3 lang5 che3 sam- tai7 kap si2-chou2 e5 su7 , choe3 au7-tai7 im5-su7 e5 kia7-a2, hoan7-le2 , ke3-hun7, siong hong-siok8 , pai7 jin5-lun5 , iau2-ku2 teh phah-sng3 i si7 seng3-kau3 iu2-kong e5 jin5-sin5 , long2 m7-chai si7 sian-ong5 e5 choe7-jin5 . Koh khah thang oan3-hun7--e5, chiu7-si7 Sek-kau3, To7-kau3 , liu5- heng5 thong-kok, hai7-lang5 phian3-lang5, i sou2 kong2 e5 iu2-hau3 long2 put-chai7 siN- cheng5 e5 hong7-iong7, iau3-kin2 si7 chai7-ti7 si2- au7 e5 che3 , pai3 , choe3-chio3, siu-chai , chhiau- tou7, pai3-put8 , liam7-keng, phah te7-gek8 ; lun7-kau3 khiok-le2, siau3-gi5 , loe7-chek, te7- chu2-chit , hau3-keng3, i2-kip8 hoan7-na7 lun7- khi2 lang5 hok8-sai7 pe7-bu2 e5 tai7-chi3--e5 , it- khai3 bo5 kong2-khi2 ; sou2-i2 i-e5 oe7 hou7 lang5 koe7 hoaN-hi2, in-ui7 bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 kou2-le2 e5 khu-sok ; tui3 an2-ni lang5-lang5 siu7 i be5- hek8, poe7 sian-ong5 ka3 lang5 iu2-hau3 e5 ho2- sim, chi2-u7 siu2 Sek-kau3 To7-kau3 e5 iN7-toan sia5-soat, i2-kip8 sian-ong5 lip8-che3 e5 le2-lou7, gong7-gong7 phah-sng3 na7 oe7 an2-ni , chiu7 thang sng3 choe3 iu2-hau3 , hai3-ah ! ChaiN2- iuN7 khoaN3 iu2-hau3 kau3-chiah sio2-khoa2, kau3-chiah khoai3 ? Lun7-kau3 goan2 seng3- kau3 tiong e5 lang5 chin-chiaN3 u7 hap8 sian- ong5 ka3 lang5 iu2-hau3 e5 ho2-sim, put-ko3 bo5 siu2 i lip8-che3 e5 le2-lou7, lang5 chiu7 kio3 goan2 choe3 than3-hoan , bo5-kong bo5-chou2 , kam2 m7-si7 oan-ong2 mah ? Lun7 che3, put-ko3 si7 ka3-lang5 iu2-hau3 e5 hoat-tou7 na7-tiaN7 , na7 oe7 iu2-hau3 chiu7 kau3-giah8, lang5 na7 oe7 than3 goan2 e5 to7-li2, jip8 goan2 e5 kau3, sin3 goan2 e5 seng3-keng , chu7-jian5 siong5-siong5 oe7 iu2- hau3 . mih-sai2 tek-khak tioh8 che3 ah ? Phi3- lun7 tang-thiN chheng7 hiu5 , he7-thiN chheng7 koah , che si7 cha2 e5 khoan2; taN na7 m7 chheng7 hiu5 beh chheng7 ni5-saN, m7 chheng7 koah beh chheng7 kang-sai , thai2-tho2