  2 . Che3 tsou2-kong hoan2-tng2 si7 tek-tsoe7 Siong7-te3 
  SaN chheng goa7 ni5 cheng5 Siong7-te3 pun2- sin ti7 Se-nai2-soaN thoan5 tsap8 kai3 , hit e5 te7 ji7 kai3 kong2, ¡§ Boh8-tit tiau-khek ngou2-siong7 , thiN-teng2 toe7-e7, tsui2-tiong pah-hang7 mih8, boh8-tit tsng-siong7 chhin-chhiuN7 i, boh8-tit pai3 kui7 , boh8-tit hok8-sai7 ; in-ui7 goa2 Ia5-ho5- hoa lin2-e5 Siong7-te3 , toan3-toan3 boe7 iong5-- tit eng7 pat8-e5 Siong7-te3 kap goa2 pi2 ; oan3- hun7 goa2 e5 lang5 , kang3 tsai-e7 hou7--i , tui3 pe7 kau3 kiaN2 kau3 saN si3 tai7 , thiaN3 goa2 , siu2 goa2 kai3-lut8 e5 lang5 chiu7 kang3 hok-khi3 hou7--i , kau3 chheng pah-tai7 ¡¨ . An2-ni , che3 , pai3 , tioh8 Siong7-te3 chiah oe7 kham-tit siu7, lang5 che3 pat8-mih8 , pai3 pat8-mih8 , chiu7 pai3 e5 lang5 , che3 e5 lang5 , i2-kip8 siu7 che3 , siu7 pai3 e5 lang5 , Siong7-te3 long2 beh heng5-hoat8--i . I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3 hian3-che3 Siong7-te3 , iah8 hian3-che3 pat8-mih8 , Siong7-te3 toa7 siu7-khi3 , kang3 chai-e7 ti7 in-e5 kok . Hi-lut8 ong5 hou7 i-e5 peh-siN3 chheng i choe3 Siong7-te3 , Hi- lut8 hoaN-hi2 , Siong7-te3 hou7 thang5 ka7-si2--i . ( Heng7-toan7 12 : 22 , 23 . ) Ko-ni5-liu5 beh pai3 Pi2-tek , Pi2-tek kin2-kin2 hu5 i kong2 , ¡§ Khi2--lai5 , goa2 iah8-si7 lang5 . ¡¨ Lou7-su7-tek e5 lang5 beh che3 Po2-lo5 , Po2-lo5 chhut-lat8 chou2- tong3 , m7-kaN2 siu7 in che3 . ( Heng7-toan7 14 : 13-18 . ) Su3-tou5 Iok-han7 beh pai3 chi2-si7 i e5 thiN-sai3 , thiN-sai3 chou2-chi2--i kong2 , ¡§ M7-thang , li2 chheng-chheng tioh8 pai3 Siong7- te3 . ¡¨ ( Bek8-si7-liok8 22 : 8 , 9 . ) Mou5-kui2 kah Ia5-sou pai3--i , Ia5-sou in2 seng3-keng e5 oe7 kong2 , ¡§ Tioh8 pai3 Chu2 li2 e5 Siong7-te3 , tok8- tok8 hok8-sai7--i . ¡¨ ( Sin-beng7-ki3 6 : 13 , Ma2- thai3 4 : 10 . ) An2-ni toa7 e5 su3-tou5, seng3 e5 thiN-sai3 , am3-se3 e5 jin5-kun, siong7-chhiaN2 m7-thang pai3 , ho5-hong3 si2-liau2 e5 lang5 . In- ui7 Siong7-te3 si7 chi3-chun bu5 tui3 , tok8-it bu5 ji7 , ban7-lang5 oa2-kho3 i lai5 oah8 , lai5 tin2-tang7 , lai5 ti7-teh , hong5-te3 e5 siN3-mia7 si7 kho3 i chiah oah8 , pe7-bu2 e5 siN3-m